00:37:49.472 --> 00:37:50.958
Segunda.

00:37:50.958 --> 00:37:51.878
¿Segundo?

00:37:53.558 --> 00:37:54.717
Porque creo que

00:37:54.958 --> 00:37:56.918
madre y mis hermanas

00:37:56.918 --> 00:37:58.438
